sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant TG as Telegram
    participant RT as Runtime
    participant Session
    participant Turn as turn.Machine
    participant Face as Face / Governor
    participant Tools

    User->>TG: DM / media / voice
    TG->>RT: InboundMessage
    RT->>Session: load + lock + scope
    RT->>RT: extract media + parse floor
    RT->>Turn: build coordinator + ports
    Turn->>Face: system prompt + history + advisory
    Face->>Tools: tool calls as needed
    Tools-->>Face: tool results
    Face-->>Turn: proposal + brokerage note
    Turn->>Turn: render visible scene
    Turn->>Session: persist scene + floor + sidecars
    Turn->>TG: deliver text / media / voice
    TG->>User: visible reply
    Turn-->>RT: turn result
    RT->>RT: process-level follow-up
